        <fields>
            <name>GuidanceMeasureDetails</name>
            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Approved Phase Measures&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;In the table below, you should see a list of your approved and completed Phase Requests. Please select the Phase Request you wish to change the measures for.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Within the Phase you have selected, you will see a separate section per measure type included. You can then amend the number of that measure in the ‘Updated Measure KPI’. If you wish to ad a new measure type to the Phase, please select the ‘+Add’ button. If you wish to remove a measure type from the Phase, please set the ‘Updated Measure KPI’ for the measure type you wish to remove as 0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt; Please be reminded:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Grant recipients should refer to the Scheme Guidance to ensure that measures meet scheme eligibility (Section 2.9, pg. 23).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
            <fieldType>DisplayText</fieldType>
            <styleProperties>
                <verticalAlignment>
                    <stringValue>top</stringValue>
                </verticalAlignment>
                <width>
                    <stringValue>12</stringValue>
                </width>
            </styleProperties>
        </fields>
        <fields>
            <name>DisplayText</name>
